---
tags:
  - proxmox
  - proxmox/container
  - proxmox/lxc
type: proxmox/container
vmid: {{ ct.vmid }}
node: "{{ ct.node | default(node) }}"
status: "{{ ct.status }}"
ip_address: "{{ networks[0].ip | default('N/A') if networks else 'N/A' }}"
cpu_cores: {{ config.cores | default(0) }}
memory_mb: {{ config.memory | default(0) }}
last_synced: "{{ synced_at }}"
---

# {{ ct.name | default("CT " ~ ct.vmid) }}

{% if ct.status == 'running' %}
> [!success] Running
> Container {{ ct.vmid }} is running on [[{{ ct.node | default(node) }}]]. Uptime: {{ uptime_str }}.
{% elif ct.status == 'stopped' %}
> [!warning] Stopped
> Container {{ ct.vmid }} is stopped.
{% else %}
> [!danger] {{ ct.status | default('Unknown') | capitalize }}
> Container {{ ct.vmid }} status: {{ ct.status | default('unknown') }}.
{% endif %}

## Overview

| Property | Value |
| --- | --- |
| CTID | {{ ct.vmid }} |
| Node | [[{{ ct.node | default(node) }}]] |
| Status | {{ ct.status }} |
| Uptime | {{ uptime_str }} |

## Configuration

| Property | Value |
| --- | --- |
| CPU Cores | {{ config.cores | default("N/A") }} |
| Memory | {{ config.memory | default("N/A") }} MB |
| Swap | {{ config.swap | default("N/A") }} MB |
| OS Template | {{ config.ostemplate | default("N/A") }} |
| Hostname | {{ config.hostname | default("N/A") }} |
| Unprivileged | {{ "Yes" if config.unprivileged | default(false) else "No" }} |
| OnBoot | {{ "Yes" if config.onboot | default(false) else "No" }} |

{% if networks %}
## Network Interfaces

| Device | Bridge | IP | Gateway | HWADDR |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
{% for nic in networks %}
| {{ nic.name }} | {{ nic.bridge | default("N/A") }} | {{ nic.ip | default("N/A") }} | {{ nic.gw | default("N/A") }} | {{ nic.hwaddr | default("N/A") }} |
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if mountpoints %}
## Mount Points

| ID | Volume | Size | Mount Path |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
{% for mp in mountpoints %}
| {{ mp.id }} | {{ mp.volume | default("N/A") }} | {{ mp.size | default("N/A") }} | {{ mp.mp | default("N/A") }} |
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if firewall_rules %}
## Firewall Rules

| Pos | Type | Action | Source | Dest | Proto | DPort | Comment | Enabled |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
{% for rule in firewall_rules %}
| {{ rule.pos | default("N/A") }} | {{ rule.type | default("N/A") }} | {{ rule.action | default("N/A") }} | {{ rule.source | default("any") }} | {{ rule.dest | default("any") }} | {{ rule.proto | default("N/A") }} | {{ rule.dport | default("N/A") }} | {{ rule.comment | default("") }} | {{ "Yes" if rule.enabled | default(true) else "No" }} |
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if snapshots %}
## Snapshots

| Name | Description | Date |
| --- | --- | --- |
{% for snap in snapshots %}
| {{ snap.name }} | {{ snap.description | default("") }} | {{ snap.snaptime | default("N/A") }} |
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if config.description %}
## Notes

{{ config.description }}
{% endif %}
